Package: SurveyStat
Type: Package
Title: Survey Data Cleaning, Weighting, Analysis and Visualization
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "SurveyStat", 
           family = "Development Team", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "surveystat@example.com")
Description: A comprehensive R package for survey data management including data cleaning, 
    survey weighting application, descriptive and inferential statistical analysis, and 
    publication-quality visualization. The package follows classical statistical methods 
    and is designed for reproducible research workflows.
